     Drive license doc: Centurion, South Africa · +27 64 699 9877 · AED 986.
2) RSSI PROXIMITY (replaces RuView). assets/js/proximity.js — REAL, no simulation:
   Web Bluetooth LE scanning reads real advertisement RSSI → counts nearby radios,
   buckets by distance (near/mid/far), estimates PEOPLE NEARBY from near-range density.
   Honest fallback when the browser can't scan; optional Ionity ESP32 edge-node endpoint
   for hardware-grade RSSI. Verified: honest "BLE SCAN UNSUPPORTED" state in browsers
   without the capability — never a fabricated count.
3) ANOTHER REMARKABLE FEATURE. assets/js/sensor-node.js — "your browser is an Ionity
   edge node": live REAL sensors — accelerometer, gyro/tilt/compass, ambient light,
   microphone sound level — visualised with a live horizon/level. On-brand AIoT sensing.
4) Adventure is now 10 acts: Enter · Native-AI · Capabilities · Audit · Edge Scan ·
   Proximity · Sensor Node · AEDi · Founder · Begin.
Verified (v2): brand tokens render (#0079E3/#FF9500), official wordmark renders in hero,
